data.description: This 3 bedroom home offers a modernized living experience in a relaxed setting. Each detail has been carefully attended to, featuring a contemporary kitchen boasting sleek blue cabinetry, subway tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances; a rejuvenated bathroom with chic dark tiling, and a comforting neutral palette. The home is adorned with laminated wood flooring throughout, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  The property enjoys an abundance of natural light and offers a versatile floor plan with ample indoor and outdoor space perfect for entertainment and leisure. Step outside to discover two expansive patios: the shaded front deck presents a perfect nook for morning coffees with a scenic overlook, while the private rear patio promises endless enjoyment with its ample space for grilling, lounging, and al fresco dining under the sun-drenched sky. Lush foliage and mature trees create a secluded ambiance, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests.  Further benefits include fresh interior and exterior paint, ensuring a move-in ready experience. The residence also features energy-efficient double-paned windows throughout, and each room is equipped with dedicated HVAC units for optimal temperature control. Storage solutions are abundant, with built-in features and an attached garage providing space for vehicles and essentials.  Unique to this property is the potential for an Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU) with its own separate road entrance(top of the property), presenting a valuable opportunity for additional rental income or a private guest suite. Set in a peaceful neighborhood, this delightful home strikes the perfect balance between tranquil living and proximity to urban conveniences, making it an ideal sanctuary in the city.
